#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:2
msgid "NTLM 身份验证"
msgstr "NTLM Authentication"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:5
msgid "NTLM认证"
msgstr "NTLM Authentication"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:6
msgid "NTLM是NT LAN Manager的缩写，NTLM是基于挑战/应答的身份验证协议，是 Windows NT 早期版本中的标准安全协议。"
msgstr "NTLM is short for NT LAN Manager. It is a challenge-response authentication protocol and was the standard security protocol in early versions of Windows NT."

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:9
msgid "基本流程"
msgstr "Basic Process"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:10
msgid "客户端在本地加密当前用户的密码成为密码散列"
msgstr "The client locally encrypts the current user's password into a password hash"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:11
msgid "客户端向服务器明文发送账号"
msgstr "The client sends the account name to the server in plaintext"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:12
msgid "服务器端产生一个16位的随机数字发送给客户端，作为一个challenge"
msgstr "The server generates a 16-digit random number and sends it to the client as a challenge"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:13
msgid "客户端用加密后的密码散列来加密challenge，然后返回给服务器，作为response"
msgstr "The client encrypts the challenge with the encrypted password hash and returns it to the server as the response"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:14
msgid "服务器端将用户名、challenge、response发送给域控制器"
msgstr "The server sends the username, challenge, and response to the domain controller"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:15
msgid "域控制器用这个用户名在SAM密码管理库中找到这个用户的密码散列，然后使用这个密码散列来加密chellenge"
msgstr "The domain controller uses the username to find the user's password hash in the SAM password database, and then uses that hash to encrypt the challenge"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:16
msgid "域控制器比较两次加密的challenge，如果一样那么认证成功，反之认证失败"
msgstr "The domain controller compares the two encrypted challenges. If they match, authentication succeeds; otherwise, authentication fails"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:19
msgid "Net-NTLMv1"
msgstr "Net-NTLMv1"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:20
msgid "Net-NTLMv1协议的基本流程如下："
msgstr "The basic process of the Net-NTLMv1 protocol is as follows:"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:22 ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:38
msgid "客户端向服务器发送一个请求"
msgstr "The client sends a request to the server"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:23
msgid "服务器接收到请求后，生成一个8位的Challenge，发送回客户端"
msgstr "After receiving the request, the server generates an 8-byte Challenge and sends it back to the client"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:24 ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:40
msgid "客户端接收到Challenge后，使用登录用户的密码hash对Challenge加密，作为response发送给服务器"
msgstr "After receiving the Challenge, the client encrypts it with the logged-in user's password hash and sends it to the server as the response"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:25 ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:41
msgid "服务器校验response"
msgstr "The server verifies the response"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:27
msgid "Net-NTLMv1 response的计算方法为"
msgstr "The Net-NTLMv1 response is calculated as follows:"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:29
msgid "将用户的NTLM hash补零至21字节分成三组7字节数据"
msgstr "Pad the user's NTLM hash with zeros to 21 bytes and split it into three 7-byte groups"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:30
msgid "三组数据作为3DES加密算法的三组密钥，加密Server发来的Challenge"
msgstr "Use the three groups as three keys for the 3DES encryption algorithm to encrypt the Challenge sent by the server"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:32
msgid "这种方式相对脆弱，可以基于抓包工具和彩虹表爆破工具进行破解。"
msgstr "This approach is relatively weak and can be cracked with packet capture tools and rainbow table cracking tools."

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:35
msgid "Net-NTLMv2"
msgstr "Net-NTLMv2"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:36
msgid "自Windows Vista起，微软默认使用Net-NTLMv2协议，其基本流程如下："
msgstr "Since Windows Vista, Microsoft has used the Net-NTLMv2 protocol by default. Its basic process is as follows:"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:39
msgid "服务器接收到请求后，生成一个16位的Challenge，发送回客户端"
msgstr "After receiving the request, the server generates a 16-byte Challenge and sends it back to the client"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:44
msgid "Hash"
msgstr "Hash"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:47
msgid "LM Hash"
msgstr "LM Hash"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:48
msgid ""
"LM Hash(LAN Manager Hash) 是windows最早用的加密算法，由IBM设计。LM Hash "
"使用硬编码秘钥的DES，且存在缺陷。早期的Windows系统如XP、Server 2003等使用LM Hash，而后的系统默认禁用了LM "
"Hash并使用NTLM Hash。"
msgstr ""
"LM Hash (LAN Manager Hash) was the earliest encryption algorithm used by"
" Windows and was designed by IBM. LM Hash uses DES with a hard-coded key and "
"has known weaknesses. Early Windows systems such as XP and Server 2003 used "
"LM Hash, while later systems disabled LM Hash by default and used NTLM Hash."

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:50
msgid "LM Hash的计算方式为："
msgstr "LM Hash is calculated as follows:"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:52
msgid "转换用户的密码为大写，14字节截断"
msgstr "Convert the user's password to uppercase and truncate it to 14 bytes"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:53
msgid "不足14字节则需要在其后添加0×00补足"
msgstr "If it is shorter than 14 bytes, append 0x00 bytes to pad it"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:54
msgid "将14字节分为两段7字节的密码"
msgstr "Split the 14 bytes into two 7-byte password blocks"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:55
msgid "以 ``KGS!@#$%`` 作为秘钥对这两组数据进行DES加密，得到16字节的哈希"
msgstr "Use ``KGS!@#$%`` as the key to DES-encrypt the two groups of data, producing a 16-byte hash"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:56
msgid "拼接后得到最后的LM Hash。"
msgstr "Concatenate the results to obtain the final LM Hash."

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:58
msgid "作为早期的算法，LM Hash存在着诸多问题："
msgstr "As an early algorithm, LM Hash has many problems:"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:60
msgid "密码长度不会超过14字符，且不区分大小写"
msgstr "Password length cannot exceed 14 characters, and case is ignored"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:61
msgid "如果密码长度小于7位，后一组哈希的值确定，可以通过结尾为 ``aad3b435b51404ee`` 来判断密码长度不超过7位"
msgstr "If the password length is less than 7 characters, the value of the second hash block is fixed, so an ending of ``aad3b435b51404ee`` can indicate that the password is no longer than 7 characters"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:62
msgid "分组加密极大程度降低了密码的复杂度"
msgstr "Block-based encryption greatly reduces password complexity"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:63
msgid "DES算法强度低"
msgstr "The DES algorithm is weak"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:66
msgid "NTLM Hash"
msgstr "NTLM Hash"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:67
msgid "为了解决LM Hash的安全问题，微软于1993年在Windows NT 3.1中引入了NTLM协议。"
msgstr "To address the security problems of LM Hash, Microsoft introduced the NTLM protocol in Windows NT 3.1 in 1993."

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:69
msgid ""
"Windows 2000 / XP / 2003 在密码超过14位前使用LM Hash，在密码超过14位后使用NTLM "
"Hash。而之后从Vista开始的版本都使用NTLM Hash。"
msgstr ""
"Windows 2000, XP, and 2003 use LM Hash for passwords up to 14 characters and"
" NTLM Hash for passwords longer than 14 characters. Later versions starting "
"with Vista use NTLM Hash."

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:71
msgid "NTLM Hash的计算方法为："
msgstr "NTLM Hash is calculated as follows:"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:73
msgid "将密码转换为16进制，进行Unicode编码"
msgstr "Convert the password to hexadecimal and encode it as Unicode"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:74
msgid "基于MD4计算哈希值"
msgstr "Calculate the hash value with MD4"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:77
msgid "攻击"
msgstr "Attacks"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:80
msgid "Pass The Hash"
msgstr "Pass the Hash"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:81
msgid "Pass The Hash (PtH) 是攻击者捕获帐号登录凭证后，复用凭证Hash进行攻击的方式。"
msgstr "Pass the Hash (PtH) is an attack method in which an attacker captures account login credentials and reuses the credential hash."

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:83
msgid ""
"微软在2012年12月发布了针对Pass The Hash攻击的防御指导，文章中提到了一些防御方法，并说明了为什么不针对Pass The "
"Hash提供更新补丁。"
msgstr ""
"In December 2012, Microsoft published defensive guidance for Pass the Hash "
"attacks. The article describes several defense methods and explains why no "
"update patch was provided specifically for Pass the Hash."

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:86
msgid "Pass The Key"
msgstr "Pass the Key"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:87
msgid "在禁用NTLM的环境下，可以用mimikatz等工具直接获取密码。"
msgstr "In environments where NTLM is disabled, tools such as mimikatz can be used to obtain passwords directly."

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:90
msgid "NTLM Relay"
msgstr "NTLM Relay"

#: ../../source/auth/ntlm.rst:91
msgid "攻击者可以一定程度控制客户端网络的时候，可以使用中间人攻击的方式来获取权限。对客户端伪装为身份验证服务器，对服务端伪装为需要认证的客户端。"
msgstr "When an attacker can control the client network to some extent, they can use a man-in-the-middle attack to obtain privileges: impersonating an authentication server to the client and impersonating a client that needs authentication to the server."

